Package ai.skymind.pipelines.output.adapter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MultiOutputAdapter<T>
    Convert one or more input INDArray (one per output name) in to an appropriate json object representing the domain to be interpreted.
    OutputAdapter<T extends BatchOutput>
    Convert an input INDArray or FieldName list map from PMML to human readable json.
